@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title VSLA Bounded Context Map

package "VSLA Service" {
    [Group Lifecycle] as GL #LightBlue
    [Capital & Shares] as CS #LightGreen
    [Internal Lending] as IL #LightYellow
    [External Funding] as EF #LightCoral
    [Group Accounting] as GA #LightGray
    [Membership & Governance] as MG #Plum
    [Mobile & Payments] as MP #LightPink
}

package "Fineract Core" as Fineract {
    [Clients] as F_Clients
    [Savings Accounts] as F_Savings
    [Loans] as F_Loans
    [Accounting GL] as F_Acc
}

GL --> CS : publishes (SelfFundedGroupCreated, MemberEnrolled, MeetingHeld)
CS --> IL : publishes (SharesPurchased)
IL --> GA : publishes (InternalLoanRepaid)
EF --> GA : publishes (ExternalFundingReceived)
MG --> GL : reads (UserGroupMapping)
MP --> CS : commands
MP --> IL : commands

CS ..> F_Savings : ACL (Outbox)
IL ..> F_Savings : ACL (AccountTransfer)
EF ..> F_Loans : ACL (Outbox)
GA ..> F_Acc : ACL (JournalEntry)
GL ..> F_Clients : ACL (Outbox)

note right of GL
  **Upstream Context**
  Drives all others
end note

note right of GA
  **Published Language**
  Subscriber to all
  monetary events
end note

note right of MP
  **Open Host Service**
  Webhooks & mobile sync
end note

@enduml
